description: This file defines the IDictionary interface and its nested interfaces INotification and IIterator within the WPEFramework::Exchange namespace. It specifies functions for managing a dictionary-like data structure, including notification registration, get/set methods, and iteration capabilities.

classes.name: IDictionary
classes.description: Interface for dictionary management with methods for registration, access, and iteration over key-value pairs.

classes.name: IDictionary::INotification
classes.description: Interface for notification callbacks when the dictionary's content is modified.

classes.name: IDictionary::IIterator
classes.description: Interface for iterating over the entries within a specific namespace in the dictionary.

methods.name: Modified
methods.description: Called when a value in a namespace is changed, indicating the namespace, key, and new value.

methods.name: Reset
methods.description: Resets the iterator to its initial state for traversal.

methods.name: IsValid
methods.description: Checks if the current iterator position is valid.

methods.name: Next
methods.description: Advances the iterator to the next element.

methods.name: Key
methods.description: Returns the key at the current iterator position.

methods.name: Value
methods.description: Returns the value at the current iterator position.

methods.name: Register
methods.description: Registers a notification sink for a specific namespace.

methods.name: Unregister
methods.description: Unregisters a notification sink from a specific namespace.

methods.name: Get
methods.description: Retrieves the value associated with a key in a namespace.

methods.name: Set
methods.description: Sets the value for a key within a namespace.

methods.name: Get (IIterator)
methods.description: Gets an iterator for a specific namespace.

ctags.name: IDictionary
ctags.pattern: /^    struct EXTERNAL IDictionary : virtual public Core::IUnknown {$/

ctags.name: IIterator
ctags.pattern: /^        struct EXTERNAL IIterator : virtual public Core::IUnknown {$/

ctags.name: INotification
ctags.pattern: /^        struct EXTERNAL INotification : virtual public Core::IUnknown {$/
